quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,Nuuni Ndahiye ikaramu n’ibyo (abamalayika n’abantu) bandika
  68,2,"Ku bw’ingabire za Nyagasani wawe (z’ubutumwa wahawe), ntabwo wowe (Muhamadi) uri umusazi"
  68,3,Kandi mu by’ukuri uzahabwa ibihembo bidashira (ku bw’ingorane uhura na zo)
  68,4,Rwose mu by’ukuri ufite ubupfura buhambaye
  68,5,"Bityo vuba aha bidatinze uzabona, n’abo (abahakanyi) babone"
  68,6,Umusazi muri mwe (uwo ari we)
  68,7,"Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wawe ni We uzi neza uwayobye inzira ye, kandi ni na We uzi neza abayobotse"
  68,8,"Bityo, ntukumvire abahinyura"
  68,9,Bifuje ko waborohera (ukabakorera ibyo bashaka) na bo bakakorohera (ntibakurwanye)
  68,10,Kandi ntukumvire buri (muntu) urahira kenshi unasuzuguritse
  68,11,"Umuneguzi wa cyane, unabunza amagambo (agenda asebanya)"
  68,12,"Ubuza ibyiza, urengera, umunyacyaha"
  68,13,"Uw’umutima winangiye, hejuru y’ibyo akaba ari ikinyendaro (atazwi inkomoko ye kwa se)"
  68,14,Yitwaza ko afite umutungo mwinshi n’urubyaro (rwinshi)
  68,15,"Iyo asomewe amagambo yacu, aravuga ati “Ni inkuru z’abo hambere.”"
  68,16,Tuzamushyiraho ikimenyetso ku mutonzi (ku zuru rye)
  68,17,"Mu by’ukuri (abantu b’i Maka), twarabagerageje nk’uko twagerageje abantu bari bafite umurima ubwo barahiraga ko rwose bawusarura mu rukerera"
  68,18,"Ariko ntibavuze (In-sha-Allah, Imana nibishaka)"
  68,19,"Bityo, ikiza (inkongi y’umuriro) giturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe kirawugota, mu gihe bo bari baryamye"
  68,20,(Umurima wabo) uhinduka nk’uruhira
  68,21,Nuko bucyeye barahamagarana
  68,22,Bagira bati “Nimuzindukire mu murima wanyu niba mugikomeje umugambi wo kuwusarura. ”
  68,23,Nuko bagenda bongorerana
  68,24,(Bagira bati) “Uyu munsi ntihagire umukene n’umwe uwubinjiranamo (umurima)
  68,25,Nuko bazinduka baganayo (mu murima wabo) biyumvamo ubushobozi (bwo kwima abakene)
  68,26,Maze bawubonye baravuga bati “Mu by’ukuri twayobye (inzira)!”
  68,27,Ahubwo twimwe (umusaruro wawo kubera umugambi wacu mubi wo kwima abakene)
  68,28,"Ushyira mu gaciro muri bo aravuga ati “Sinari nababwiye ko iyo muza gusingiza (Allah mukanamushimira, mukanavuga muti: In-sha-Allah, mutari guhura n’ibi byago)?”"
  68,29,"Baravuga bati “Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani wacu, mu by’ukuri twari inkozi z’ibibi!”"
  68,30,Nuko bamwe batangira guhindukirira abandi (bitana bamwana) bavebana
  68,31,Baravuga bati “Mbega ishyano tubonye! Mu by’ukuri twari abarengera (imbibi za Allah).”
  68,32,Hari ubwo Nyagasani wacu yadushumbusha (umurima) mwiza kuwuruta. Rwose twerekeje ibyifuzo byacu kwa Nyagasani wacu
  68,33,"Uko ni ko ibihano (bya Allah ku isi) bimera! Ariko ibihano byo ku munsi w’imperuka birahambaye cyane, iyaba bari babizi"
  68,34,Mu by’ukuri abagandukira (Allah) bazagororerwa Ijuru ryuje ingabire kwa Nyagasani wabo
  68,35,Ese abicisha bugufi imbere ya Allah (Abayisilamu) twabafata kimwe n’inkozi z’ibibi
  68,36,Ese mwabaye mute? Mubona ibintu mute
  68,37,Cyangwa mwaba mufite igitabo musomamo (ko abicisha bugufi ari kimwe n’inkozi z’ibibi)
  68,38,Mu by’ukuri mukaba mufitemo (muri icyo gitabo) aho mukura ibyo
  68,39,Cyangwa mudufiteho amasezerano ntakuka afite agaciro kugeza ku munsi w’imperuka yo kuzabona ibyo mwifuza
  68,40,Babaze (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ni nde muri bo wabyishingira (akabibera umuhamya)?”
  68,41,Cyangwa se (abahakanyi) baba bafite ibigirwamana (bizabafasha ku munsi w’imperuka)? Ngaho nibazane ibyo bigirwamana byabo niba ari abanyakuri
  68,42,"(Ibuka) umunsi (ibintu bizaba bikomeye kandi biteye ubwoba), ubwo igice cyo hepfo cy’ukuguru (kwa Allah) kizagaragarizwa (ibiremwa), nuko (abahakanyi) bagahamagarirwa kubamira (Allah) ariko ntibabishobore"
  68,43,"Bazaba bubitse amaso (kubera ikimwaro), batwikiriwe n’ugusuzugurika. Nyamara bajyaga bahamagarirwa kubamira Allah ari bazima (ntibabikore kubera ubwibone)"
  68,44,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) ndekera uwo ari we wese uhinyura iyi nkuru (Qur’an). Rwose (abo bayihinyura) tuzabatwara buhoro buhoro (tubaganisha mu bihano) mu buryo batazi"
  68,45,Nzanabaha igihe (bibwire ko batazahanwa); mu by’ukuri imigambi yanjye irakomeye
  68,46,"Cyangwa (bibwira ko wowe Muhamadi) ubasaba igihembo, none bakaba baremererwa n’ubwishyu"
  68,47,"Ahubwo se bibwira ko bazi ibitagaragara, bakaba babishingiraho bandika (ibyo bishakiye, badakeneye ibyo ubabwira)"
  68,48,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kandi ntube nk’umwe wamizwe n’ifi (Umuhanuzi Yunusu) ubwo yadutakambiraga n’agahinda kenshi"
  68,49,"Iyo bitaza kuba ingabire iturutse kwa Nyagasani we yamugezeho, (ifi) yari kumuruka ku musenyi wo ku nkombe kandi umugayo umuriho"
  68,50,"Nuko Nyagasani we aramutoranya, maze amushyira mu ntungane"
  68,51,"Kandi iyo abahakanye bumvise urwibutso (Qur’an), bakurebesha indoro ikomeye, bifuza ko wagwa igihunga kugira ngo bavuge bati “Rwose ni umusazi.”"
  68,52,Kandi (Qur’an) nta kindi iri cyo usibye kuba ari urwibutso ku biremwa byose